{
  "stem": "27409.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had to-- every-- every unit which needed soldiers, they came 200 solider, a 100 soldiers, so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a unit, which needed 500 soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was already in connection with the other unit to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I sent them off with this other unit outside the town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I took them to the station sent them off, for when coming back they were searching for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This [INAUDIBLE] a partisan with a-- goes with a sub-machine gun around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he took the men out of town where they disappeared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I have sent them off to the unit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were supposed to go to [NON-ENGLISH] for work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were Ukrainian, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were for the military industry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I sent them off to the front because they asked me to help them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then I was called, also, when I arrested I told them Stalin told to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Comrad Stalin told all for the front, all for victory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I did my share.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They couldn't say, but Stalin said it's not-- it's wrong.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to Kiev, was sent to Kiev there to-- where they had this camp for-- training camp for the front.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was only three days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- I was hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was told that you hardly got to work to eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the day they marched-- marched forward there were march training.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They learned what I already did [INAUDIBLE] practice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so, I asked for-- to be sent to the front, [INAUDIBLE] to the front.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They send you-- me with the other group to a unit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came with [NON-ENGLISH] where I met the unit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And with this unit I went opposite [INAUDIBLE] in the forest where they're assembling for attack on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
